Summary: 3 very big & fast lights dropping & ascending
divs: Sighting Detailsstarted on the 14th of august in the west bright light very bright dropped at a right angle very fast above where a friend resides so rang them as i was establishing what id seen they too noticed it as being a cigar shape right above them before zooming off the following day at 12;30am on the 15th of august as plane was flying past to the south 2 bright lights descended at great speeds again parallel to each other behind the plane when measured against the chimney pots on the houses these things were very big
